Executables
===============================================================================

Use `mechc build` to package Mech bytecode with a Rust shim executable.

```sh
mechc build main.mec --out app
mechc build main.mec --release --out app
```

The current output path is:

```text
build/debug/app.exe
build/release/app.exe
```

This is the current artifact path, not a final cross-platform packaging contract.

For bytecode-only output, use `mech build` instead.
